{
  "text": "Each rater was provided with reference literature regarding the assessment of esophageal motility based on the CC V3.0. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] For this study, the adult cut-off criteria of the CC were used. All raters viewed an introduc- To assess intrarater reliability, each rater analyzed the dataset twice, with at least 7 days between repeat analyses. All raters were blinded to the diagnosis of the patients, and all studies were deidentified. Also to avoid the potential for sequence bias, the order of studies was randomized between raters and between repeat analyses.",
